    "trapped_gallery": {
      "location": "The Trapped Gallery",
      "scene": "A long gallery floored with worn flagstones. The stone is pocked with old puncture-marks and a row of narrow dart-slits lines one wall — somewhere underfoot a pressure plate is surely waiting. Further on, a cluster of burst puffball fungi hazes the air with drifting spores. A sealed healing draught rests in a niche by the far arch. These are dangers of the place, not foes — there is no one here to fight, only the gallery to cross.",
