      "scene": "The arch opens into a domed sanctum lit by cold witch-light. A reliquary of black glass pulses with a dread-ward — drawing near it forces a Wisdom saving throw (DC 13) or the mind buckles under supernatural fear. On the bier within rests the Pale Sigil — the relic you came for. This is the heart of the vault; there is nowhere deeper to go.",
